	(905, 'Operations Supervisor (ChemCare)', '/en/job/493397/operations-supervisor-chemcare', 'Operations', '2023-10-07 07:55:00', ' Higher NITEC / NITEC in any discipline Possess Class 3 or Class 3A license\nThe following will be highly valued: Knowledge and experience in Dangerous Goods regulation and inspection protocols Knowledge and experience of billing procedures  Experience in conducting inspections and preparing detailed reports Good organizational and time management skills, with the ability to prioritize tasks effectively Strong attention to detail and accuracy in recording and reporting information Proficient in using computer applications for data entry and report preparation'),
