	(907, 'Manager/Senior Manager (Procurement)', '/en/job/493415/managersenior-manager-procurement', 'Procurement', '2023-12-31 07:55:00', 'Bachelor\'s degree.\n5-8 years experience in procurement of corporate and spares categories, and a focus on digital, marketplace and e-procurement.\nExperience with e-procurement, SRM, KYS, spend analysis and compliance monitoring.\nStrong stakeholder engagement and effective influencing and change management skills\nStrong analytical and problem-solving skills.\nAbility to manage multiple projects simultaneously.\nEnergetic, resourceful, self-motivated and resilient.\nAbility to work independently and as part of a team.\nCompetent in negotiations and contract knowledge'),
	(908, 'Assistant Operation Executive (Pasir Panjang Automobile Terminal)', '/en/job/493414/assistant-operation-executive-pasir-panjang-automobile-terminal', 'Operations', '2023-12-31 07:55:00', 'Diploma in Logistics / Supply Chain Management. Other disciplines with experience in logistics operations management preferable in 3rd party logistics, distribution or manufacturing environment will also be considered\nProficient in MS Office\nAble to work independently\nGood communication skills\nWilling to perform 12 hours shift'),
	(909, 'Finance Manager/Senior Finance Manager (Logistics)', '/en/job/493413/finance-managersenior-finance-manager-logistics', 'Finance', '2023-12-31 07:55:00', 'Possess a degree in Accountancy and at least 10 years experience of relevant experience, of which at least 5 years\' are in the logistics industry\nStrong analytical skills and sharp commercial and business acumen\nGood business partnering skills\nExcellent communication skills - both written and verbal'),
	(910, 'Assistant / Deputy Manager / Manager (Port+ Commercial)', '/en/job/493303/assistant-deputy-manager-manager-port-commercial', 'Operations, Commercial', '2023-12-31 07:55:00', 'Degree in any discipline\nCritical thinking and writing skills\nReasonable numeric literacy\nBasic level of data intelligence and curiosity preferred\nGood communication and interpersonal skills\nAdaptability and resilience; able to react nimbly to dynamic changes in customer demands and work scope\nHas keen interest to learn'),
	(911, 'Manager (Talent Acquisition)', '/en/job/493412/manager-talent-acquisition', 'Human Resource', '2023-10-31 07:55:00', ' Possess a Degree in any discipline or equivalent  At least 8 to 10 years of relevant experience with industry exposure to B2B organisations  Strong communication and interpersonal skills  Track record in supporting senior stakeholders on their business needs Possess drive and able to thrive in a dynamic environment  Results-driven and takes ownership and accountability  Experience with end-to-end HR programmes; including but not limited to leading projects,   campus recruitment fairs, recruitment branding  Strong business acumen and analytical skills Proactive and a team player'),
	(912, 'Company Driver', '/en/job/493410/company-driver', 'Admin', '2023-12-31 07:55:00', ' Possess Class 3 & Class 4 driving licence with a clean record Pleasant and polite, and be able to speak English Has prior experience driving mini bus Familiar with Singapore roads Responsible and able to maintain strict confidentiality Able to start work immediately or within short notice'),
	(913, 'Deputy Manager (Talent Acquisition)', '/en/job/493409/deputy-manager-talent-acquisition', 'Human Resource', '2023-10-31 07:55:00', '- At least 5 years\' of relevant talent acquisition experience- Good verbal, presentation, and written communication skills- Detail-oriented with strong analytical skills- A strong relationship builder who can engage effectively across diverse groups and stakeholders - Able to handle  multiple tasks concurrently in a dynamic environment- Result-driven self-starter and able to deliver in a fast-paced environment with minimal supervision- Positive, energetic and a resourceful team player- Strong interest in social media landscape and comfortable in using social media platforms for outreach- Creative and able to conceptualize compelling content with interesting and captivating visuals to engage   diverse groups- Working knowledge of editing software such as Photoshop, Adobe Premiere, Final Cut Pro etc'),
	(914, 'Accounts Assistant (AR)', '/en/job/492958/accounts-assistant-ar', 'Finance', '2023-10-31 07:55:00', 'NITEC in Accountancy or LCCI or or equivalent    \nHave at least 1 year of Book keeping experience and/or experience in AR / AP\nMust be meticulous and detailed\nCandidates applying for the above position should also possess strong analytical and communication skills, as well as team spirit and the ability to excel under pressure.'),
